languages.text: "Ты просто ничего не понимаешь... А вот она, похоже, начала. И мне нравится, как это откровение изменило ее".
"You know nothing about what makes one superior... but she is beginning to understand. And I marvel at how this revelation has changed her."

languages.text: "Ihr habt keinen Schimmer, was jemanden überlegen macht ... sie jedoch beginnt es zu verstehen. Und ich bin fasziniert, die diese Offenbarung sie verändert hat."
languages.original_text: "You know nothing about what makes one superior... but she is beginning to understand. And I marvel at how this revelation has changed her."

languages.text: « Vous ignorez tout de ce qui fait la supériorité de tel ou tel individu... mais elle, elle commence à comprendre. Et je suis émerveillé par la façon dont cette révélation l'a transfigurée. »
languages.original_text: "You know nothing about what makes one superior... but she is beginning to understand. And I marvel at how this revelation has changed her."

languages.text: «No sabes nada de superioridad... pero ella empieza a entenderla. Es una maravilla ver cómo la revelación la ha cambiado».
languages.original_text: "You know nothing about what makes one superior... but she is beginning to understand. And I marvel at how this revelation has changed her."

languages.text: 「何が人を優位に立たせるのか、お前は知らないだろうな…。だが彼女は理解し始めている。そして、この啓示が彼女をどのように変えたのか、私は驚嘆しているんだ」
languages.original_text: "You know nothing about what makes one superior... but she is beginning to understand. And I marvel at how this revelation has changed her."

languages.text: “你根本不明白地位是怎么赢来的……但她已经开始明白了。她得到的启示改变了她，这真是让我惊异不已。”
languages.original_text: "You know nothing about what makes one superior... but she is beginning to understand. And I marvel at how this revelation has changed her."

languages.text: "Birini üstün yapanın ne olduğuna dair hiçbir bilgin yok... Yine de anlamaya başlıyor. Bense bu aydınlanmanın onu nasıl değiştirdiğini hayranlıkla seyrediyorum."
